===农业废水处理===
'''非点源废水控制'''<br />
美国最大的农业污染来自农田冲刷出来的[[沉积物|沉积物]]（[[土壤|土壤]]松动）。<ref name="EPA-AGFact" />农民可以利用[[侵蚀控制|侵蚀控制]]来减少径流，保持土壤。常用的技术包括等高耕作、护盖农作物、[[轮作|轮作]]、种植[[多年生植物|多年生植物]]、设立溪流缓冲区。<ref name="NRCS-NCPS">U.S. Natural Resources Conservation Service (NRCS). Washington, DC.  [http://www.nrcs.usda.gov/wps/portal/nrcs/main/national/technical/cp/ncps/ "National Conservation Practice Standards."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nrcs.usda.gov/wps/portal/nrcs/main/national/technical/cp/ncps/ |date=20170708144234 }} National Handbook of Conservation Practices. Accessed 2015-10-02.</ref><ref name="EPA-agmm"/>{{Rp|pp. 4-95–4-96|date=May 2009}}

农田上用的常见营养物（如[[氮|氮]]和[[磷|磷]]）来自于商用[[肥料|肥料]]、动物[[有机肥|有机肥]]或市政工业废水及淤泥。营养物可以从残余农作物、[[灌溉|灌溉]]流水、[[野生动物|野生动物]]大气沉降进入径流。<ref name="EPA-agmm">{{cite report |date=July 2003 |title=National Management Measures to Control Nonpoint Source Pollution from Agriculture |url=https://www.epa.gov/polluted-runoff-nonpoint-source-pollution/national-management-measures-control-nonpoint-source-0 |publisher=EPA |id=EPA-841-B-03-004 |access-date=2017-07-28 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903013316/https://www.epa.gov/polluted-runoff-nonpoint-source-pollution/national-management-measures-control-nonpoint-source-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{Rp|p. 2–9}}农民可以进行养分管理来减少滥用肥料<ref name="NRCS-NCPS" /><ref name="EPA-agmm" />{{Rp|pp. 4-37–4-38}}及可能的富营养污染。

为减少害虫影响，农民可以使用病虫害综合治理技术（包括[[生物防治|生物防治]]）来控制害虫、减少化学杀虫剂依赖、保护水质。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.epa.gov/safepestcontrol/integrated-pest-management-ipm-principles |title=Integrated Pest Management Principles |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2015 |website=Pest Control and Pesticide Safety for Consumers |publisher=EPA |accessdate=2017-07-28 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729012539/https://www.epa.gov/safepestcontrol/integrated-pest-management-ipm-principles |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''点源废水处理'''<br />
大型牲畜和畜禽农场，如工业化农场，即“集中型动物饲养经营”或“饲养场”在美国受到越来越多的政府监管。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.epa.gov/npdes/animal-feeding-operations-afos |title=Animal Feeding Operations |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2016 |website=National Pollutant Discharge Elimination System |publisher=EPA |accessdate=2017-07-28 |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801040957/https://www.epa.gov/npdes/animal-feeding-operations-afos |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Iowa Department of Natural Resources. Des Moines, IA. [http://www.iowadnr.gov/afo/ "Animal Feeding Operations in Iowa."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iowadnr.gov/afo/ |date=20090909154407 }} Accessed March 5, 2009.</ref> 畜禽粪便在密闭的厌氧塘里处理，尔后撒入操场。人工湿地有时被用于处理动物废弃物。一些畜禽粪便和[[秸秆|秸秆]]、[[堆肥|堆肥]]一起混合后高温处理，生成无菌松脆的肥料，改良土壤。

===建筑工地控制===
[[File:Silt_fence_EPA.jpg|right]]
通过安装如下设施管理建筑工地泥沙：
* [[侵蚀控制|侵蚀控制]]：如覆盖物或喷草
* 泥沙控制：如沉砂池或拦砂网<ref>Tennessee Department of Environment and Conservation. Nashville, TN (2012). [http://tnepsc.org/handbook.asp "Tennessee Erosion and Sediment Control Handbook."] {{Wayback|url=http://tnepsc.org/handbook.asp |date=20170726133629 }}</ref>

排放有毒化学物如轮机燃料和分散混凝土预防如下：
* 防泄漏和控制计划
* 特殊设计的容器（如混凝土）和结构，如溢出控制和转移护道<ref>{{cite report |date=February 2012 |title=Concrete Washout |series=Stormwater Best Management Practice |url=https://www.epa.gov/npdes/national-menu-best-management-practices-bmps-stormwater-documents |publisher=EPA |id=EPA 833-F-11-006 |access-date=2017-07-29 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729215118/https://www.epa.gov/npdes/national-menu-best-management-practices-bmps-stormwater-documents |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===城市径流控制===
{{Main article|城市径流}}
[[File:Trounce_Pond.jpg|right]]的[[调整池|调整池]]]]
城市径流有效控制方式包括减少雨水流速流量及减少污染物排放。地方政府利用各种雨水管理技术来减少城市径流影响。这些技术在美国叫做最佳管理措施，专注于控制水量及水质。<ref name="EPA-PDS">{{cite report |date=August 1999 |title=Preliminary Data Summary of Urban Storm Water Best Management Practices |chapter=Ch. 5: Description and Performance of Storm Water Best Management Practices |url=https://www.epa.gov/eg/industrial-wastewater-studies-miscellaneous |publisher=EPA |id=EPA-821-R-99-012 |access-date=2017-07-30 |archive-date=2017-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730210640/https://www.epa.gov/eg/industrial-wastewater-studies-miscellaneous |dead-url=no }}</ref>

污染物预防措施包括[[低影响开发|低影响开发]]技术、安装[[绿化屋顶|绿化屋顶]]、优化应用化学品（如管理轮机燃油、化肥和农药）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://water.epa.gov/polwaste/npdes/swbmp/Low-Impact-Development-LID-and-Other-Green-Design-Strategies.cfm |title=Low Impact Development and Other Green Design Strategies |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219220712/http://water.epa.gov/polwaste/npdes/swbmp/Low-Impact-Development-LID-and-Other-Green-Design-Strategies.cfm |archive-date=2015-02-19 |website=National Pollutant Discharge Elimination System |publisher=EPA |access-date=2017-07-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>径流缓和系统包括渗滤池、生态调节池、建设[[湿地|湿地]]、[[调整池|调整池]]等类似设施。<ref>California Stormwater Quality Association. Menlo Park, CA. [https://www.casqa.org/resources/bmp-handbooks/municipal-bmp-handbook "Municipal BMP Handbook."] {{Wayback|url=https://www.casqa.org/resources/bmp-handbooks/municipal-bmp-handbook |date=20170629213823 }} 2003.</ref><ref>New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection. Trenton, NJ. [http://www.njstormwater.org/bmp_manual2.htm "New Jersey Stormwater Best Management Practices Manual."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.njstormwater.org/bmp_manual2.htm |date=20211122102819 }} April 2004.</ref>

城市径流的热污染可以通过雨水管理系统得以控制，系统吸收径流或将其注入[[地下水|地下水]]、如生态调节系统和渗滤池。由于在注入溪流前雨水会被阳光加热，渗滤池在调节温度上效果相对欠佳。<ref name="EPA-PDS" />{{Rp|p. 5–58|date=May 2012}}

=== 回收再用 ===
經過處理過的廢水可利用回收作為飲用水，如[[新加坡|新加坡]]；或是作為[[工業|工業]]上的使用，如[[冷卻塔|冷卻塔]]；或是用來作[[地下水補注|地下水補注]]（artificial recharge of aquifers）；或是用在[[農業|農業]]上，像[[以色列|以色列]]70%的農業[[灌溉|灌溉]]都是用高度淨化的廢水；或是如[[佛羅里達|佛羅里達]]的[[佛罗里达大沼泽地|沼澤地]]那樣，利用處理過的廢水來進行自然[[生態系統|生態系]]的修復重建工作。

